The,Civil,Rights,Data,Collection,CRDC,API,is,a,brainchild,of,the,U,S,Department,of,Education,that,allows,users,to,track,and,gather,data,concerning,the,progress,of,education,and,civil,rights,in,public,schools,It,allows,developers,to,build,apps,that,provide,access,to,a,variety,of,parameters,including,student,enrollment,chronic,absenteeism,and,out,of,school,suspension,in,public,schools,Developers,seeking,to,access,the,API,must,sign,up,for,API,keys,through,a,Github,anchored,link,provided,in,the,documentation